<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Check-In Confirmation</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/style.css">
</head>
<body onload="onload()">
  <h1><%= message %></h1>

  <% if (mood === "happy") { %>
    <h2>Since you're happy, here are some activities to try:</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Do something kind for someone else (text a friend, leave a nice comment)</li>
      <li>Start or continue a creative project</li>
      <li>Organize a small part of your room or space</li>
      <li>Try learning a fun skill or fact youâ€™ve been curious about</li>
      <li>Take a photo of something that represents today</li>
    </ul>
  <% } %>

  <% if (mood === "sad") { %>
    <h2>Since you're feeling down, here are some activities to try:</h2>
    <ul>
    <li>Watch a comfort show or video</li>
    <li>Express your emotions creatively (draw, write, paint,etc)</li>
    <li>Try a short meditation or breathing exercise</li>
    <li>Make a playlist that matches how you feel</li>
    <li>Take a long shower or do a simple skincare routine</li>
    </ul>
  <% } %>
  <% if (mood === "mad") { %>
    <h2>Since you're feeling mad, here are some activities to try:</h2>
    <ul>
    <li>Do a high-energy workout</li>
    <li>Step away from everything and try breathing excersises</li>
    <li>Listen to music that matches your mood at full volume</li>
    <li>Channel your anger into art</li>
    <li>Step outside and focus on what you can see, hear, feel</li>
    </ul>
  <% } %>
  <% if (mood === "neutral") { %>
    <h2>Since you're feeling neutral, here are some activities to try:</h2>
    <ul>
    <li>Try a five-minute declutter of your space</li>
    <li>Browse a new playlist or explore music from a different genre</li>
    <li>Take a walk and try to notice 5 things you've never paid attention to</li>
    <li>Try a short quiz or personality test just for fun</li>
    <li>Make a simple snack or drink</li>
    </ul>
  <% } %>

  <a href="/">Go back to the homepage</a>
  <!-- Directs the script.js file, allowing, as of right now, to access Dark Mode -->
  <script src="/script.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
